.TH devin-help-mcp 1  "mcp " 
.SH NAME
devin\-help\-mcp \- Connect and log in to Model Context Protocol servers
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin help mcp\fR [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Connect and log in to Model Context Protocol servers
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
devin\-help\-mcp\-add(1)
Add a new MCP server
.TP
devin\-help\-mcp\-list(1)
List all configured MCP servers
.TP
devin\-help\-mcp\-get(1)
Get details for a specific MCP server
.TP
devin\-help\-mcp\-remove(1)
Remove an MCP server
.TP
devin\-help\-mcp\-login(1)
Authenticate with an MCP server via OAuth
.TP
devin\-help\-mcp\-logout(1)
Remove stored OAuth credentials for an MCP server
.TP
devin\-help\-mcp\-enable(1)
Enable a disabled MCP server
.TP
devin\-help\-mcp\-disable(1)
Disable an MCP server without removing it
